Subject: Online referrals via website


Hi Trudy,

I hope that you are well.

Can you please help me in making small additions to both our inpatient and day program online referral forms on our website? This in in relation to the online form and NOT the "Downloadable referral form"

Inpatient Online Referral
We are wanting to include in Section 2 (Referral Details ) a required/mandatory data field box titled "Specialist's Provider Number" - positioned below the "Referring Specialist" field.
We are hoping that this can be done so that if this field is left blank then the referral cannot proceed to the next section (Fund Details).




Day Program Online Referral
We are wanting to include a required/mandatory data field box titled "Specialist's Provider Number" - positioned below the "Referring Specialist/GP" field. (Please note that there currently is a spelling error with the "T" missing at the end of "Specialist".
Again, we would like this to be designed so that if left blank then the referral cannot be successfully submitted.



Please let me know if you need any other information.

Kind regards,

Caleb Showyin
